headline: Sky Real Estate Acquires Osage Beach Outlet Marketplace
summary: Sky Real Estate is excited to announce its acquisition of the Osage Beach Outlet Marketplace from a subsidiary of Simon Property Group, Inc (NYSE: SPG). The 391,000-square-foot shopping center, located on a 60-acre parcel along Osage Beach Parkway, has been a cornerstone of the Lake of the Ozarks region for decades.
